hains it takes contracts and workers moving and being mobilized.\nMost Read from Bloomberg Businessweek\nI Have Half of MAGA The Republican Challenging Trump From Within\nA Restaurant Thats Barely Raised Prices Since 1973\nUniteds CEO Is Here to Buy Your Struggling Airline\nWhy If the War Doesnt End Soon Everyone Will Pay\nAI Startup Has Helped Reverse Thousands of Denied Health Insurance Claims\n2026 Bloomberg L.P.\nTerms\nand\nPrivacy Policy\nPrivacy Dashboard\nMore Info', additional_kwargs={}, response_metadata={})]
